Barbara Luddy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Luddy 0 Barbara Luddy (May 25, 1908 – April 1, 1979) was an American actress from Great Falls, Montana. Her film career began with silent pictures in the 1920s, during which time she was also a prolific radio performer.
